tika.dc.description: When a young woman is found horribly murdered, Detective Chief Inspector Jane Tennison has got her the last chance to prove herself. She might to work fast for catching the murderer and she would stop him killing again. But also she had to fight for win the respect of the men she has been commanded. And the men had a hope that she'd fail every step of the way. She must make no mistakes. Then a second body has been found…
